data.description: Welcome home to this Colonial nestled in the amenity-filled community of Pocono Country Place, where the perfect blend of comfort and convenience awaits your personal touch. Perfect opportunity for an investment, short term rental, vacation home or year round residence. Step into a formal living room featuring an airstone accent wall, complemented by a formal dining room on the opposite side, ideal for entertaining guests. The heart of the home lies at the back, where an open-concept family room seamlessly flows into a beautiful kitchen. The kitchen boasts modern touches, including a tile backsplash, quartz countertops, & stainless steel appliances. A convenient laundry closet adds to the practicality of daily living. Enjoy the built-in Bluetooth speakers in the lighting on the first floor. Completing the first floor is a powder room in need of completion. Upstairs discover three bedrooms & a full bathroom awaiting your finishing touch. With a fresh coat of paint, installation of some flooring and some lighting, the inside of the home transforms into a move-in-ready haven. Outside, there is large rear deck perfect for outdoor relaxation, along with the potential to add a large front deck that will offer a welcoming entrance to your home! Enjoy a lifestyle enriched by the community's outstanding amenities, including pools, clubhouses, playgrounds, basketball courts, paddle boating, bocce ball, lake beach, fishing, and the peace of 24/7 gated security. Home is being sold as is.
